  <summary date="2019-08-23T12:55:08Z" status="Introduced in House">Keith Nolan Air Force Deaf Demonstration Act of 2018

This bill requires the U.S. Air Force to (1) carry out a demonstration program assessing the advisability of permitting individuals with auditory impairments to act as officers, and (2) report to Congress as to the program's outcome.</summary>
